      <description>&lt;p&gt;What’s so awful about being called a couch potato? According to experts, a couch potato implies that the individual simply sits in a couch watching television, reading, or playing video games and not doing any type of exercise to stay fit. As a response there happen to be fairly a number of gadgets that have [...]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A post from: &lt;a href="http://exercisesfortheelderly.org/"&gt;Exercises For The Elderly&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/how-seniors-have-fun-exercises-for-the-elderly/How_Seniors_Have_Fun-_Exercises_for_The_Elderly-Venturing_Outside_the_Box_to_Assist_Couch_Potatoes_to_Begin_Living_Healthier.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>What’s so awful about being called a couch potato? According to experts, a couch potato implies that the individual simply sits in a couch watching television, reading, or playing video games and not doing any type of exercise to stay fit. As a response there happen to be fairly a number of gadgets that have been produced just for people who do not want to get up from their comfortable positions. Well, there’s truly no pleasing the difficult core expert experts who think the gadgets are really not a great option to being in a fitness center or doing sports.</p>
<p>Fortunately, you will find more experts who think in doing half actions. With the <a href="http://www.myflexbeltreview.com/" target='_blank'>flexbelt</a> mini dumbbells, as well as massage chairs, muscles are obtaining some degree of workout. It’s not perfect, but it’s far better than no exercise in any way. In fact some of these <a href="http://www.myflexbeltreview.com/best-ab-exercises-to-complement-using-the-flex-belt/" target='_blank'>best ab machines</a> have been a constructive impact.</p>
<p>If you talk to many public wellness experts who do not possess the budget to invest on fitness center gear and memberships, this type of equipment is really a instrument and can be efficient. In Canada a research was carried out in 2008 by the Canadian Community Health Survey which directly associated obesity to couch potatoes and watching television daily for hours. </p>
<p>These people will never voluntarily step into rubber shoes to go jogging, or drive to a fitness center and spend to sweat. They’d rather view their television programs, drive towards the supermarket for supplies or perhaps call in for food delivery instead of miss their favorite programs.  They do not judge and would favor to not be judged. They are law-abiding citizens and spend their taxes so becoming a couch potato is really a individual option. </p>
<p>One method to snap them from their mode of living would be to provide them something to accomplish with their hands with out taking them away from their favorite sport &#8211; sitting. You can appeal to their emotional side and get them to complete the mini workout for you personally. You can even get it done together. It will assist you to comprehend them better and they&#8217;ll learn to open their minds to doing something other than staying physically idle.</p>
<p>An additional idea would be to get them a mobile television. These are mobile phones that they can consider with them every time they&#8217;ve to step out. It might not have cable television but you can tap into the nearby stations or use the internet to stream television programs.  In short, 1 has to be creative and come up with options that have over a 50% possibility of succeeding.</p>
<p>A post from: <a href="http://exercisesfortheelderly.org/">Exercises For The Elderly</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
